Fun stream as per usual. But here's a little tidbit of info that makes it even more funnier:
Apparently you actually can't cook grenades in this game (run the fuse out before throwing).

In other words, there was actually no reason for Gura to panic over tossing that grenade since it doesn't begin the countdown until after you throw it. :_Sometimes:
